<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:13:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着美联储焦点的加强，股市小幅走低，美元坚挺；加密货币飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-21/</link><description>周二，亚洲股市走低，而美元坚挺，因投资者等待美联储最新政策会议纪要，以评估今年可能降息的时机和程度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 03:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>美元稳定；以太坊推动加密货币反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-ether-fuels-crypto-rally-2024-05-21/</link><description>周二美元坚挺，而日元则在 156 水平的弱侧挣扎，但交易大多区间波动，因为投资者普遍坚持对美联储今年降息的预期时间和幅度的看法。</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 May 2024 00:53:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-ether-fuels-crypto-rally-2024-05-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：亚洲股市有望创 2021 年以来最佳表现</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-20/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 21:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>贝莱德举报人因解雇、关闭中国监控工具而提起诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/blackrock-whistleblower-alleges-cover-up-search-engine-spot-chinese-investments-2024-05-20/</link><description>贝莱德被一位举报的前副总裁起诉，索赔 2000 万美元，他表示，在他反对同事的自我交易后，贝莱德解雇了他，并被迫关闭了一个用于监控客户有关非法投资（包括在中国）讨论的搜索引擎。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 16:42:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/blackrock-whistleblower-alleges-cover-up-search-engine-spot-chinese-investments-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>参议院报告称，宝马向美国进口了 8,000 辆汽车，其零部件来自被禁止的中国供应商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-imported-8000-vehicles-into-us-with-parts-banned-chinese-supplier-senate-2024-05-20/</link><description>美国参议院周一发布的一份报告称，德国汽车制造商宝马向美国进口了至少 8,000 辆 Mini Cooper 汽车，其电子元件来自被禁止的中国供应商。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 13:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-imported-8000-vehicles-into-us-with-parts-banned-chinese-supplier-senate-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：随着美国发货平息投机者的狂热，铜的创纪录运行面临风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/coppers-record-run-risk-us-shipments-calm-speculator-frenzy-2024-05-20/</link><description>未来几周，铜价飙升至历史新高的势头可能无法持续，行动主要集中在运送材料以弥补美国商品交易所期货市场暴露的空头头寸，而不是最大消费国中国的不温不火的需求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 13:19:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/coppers-record-run-risk-us-shipments-calm-speculator-frenzy-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>价格创历史新高时有关铜市场的主要事实</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/main-facts-about-copper-market-prices-hit-record-highs-2024-05-20/</link><description>周一，由于空头回补引发的近期反弹，为投机者和基金押注金属价格上涨创造了动力，铜价飙升至历史新高。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 12:55:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/main-facts-about-copper-market-prices-hit-record-highs-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：“Nvidia 周”开局活跃</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-20/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 10:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，中国房价暴跌，今年销售状况将恶化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/slump-chinas-home-prices-sales-set-worsen-this-year-2024-05-20/</link><description>路透调查显示，随着房地产投资和销售下滑​​加剧，今年中国房价将以更快的速度下跌，这对正在加倍努力重振受危机打击的房地产行业的政策制定者来说是一个沉重的提醒。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:54:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/slump-chinas-home-prices-sales-set-worsen-this-year-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>经济复苏乏力，1-4月中国财政收入下降2.7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fiscal-revenue-shrank-27-jan-april-amid-shaky-economic-recovery-2024-05-20/</link><description>继1月至3月下滑2.3%后，2024年前4个月中国财政收入同比下滑2.7%，进一步表明经济复苏不平衡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-fiscal-revenue-shrank-27-jan-april-amid-shaky-economic-recovery-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>面对华为的激烈竞争，苹果在中国大幅下调 iPhone 价格</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-slashes-iphone-prices-china-amid-fierce-huawei-competition-2024-05-20/</link><description>苹果公司在其中国天猫官方网站上推出了大幅折扣活动，部分 iPhone 型号最高可享受 2,300 元（318 美元）的折扣。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:22:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-slashes-iphone-prices-china-amid-fierce-huawei-competition-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>奥迪与上汽集团合作开发中国专用电动汽车平台</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/audi-partner-saic-develop-china-specific-ev-platform-2024-05-20/</link><description>大众汽车旗下高端品牌奥迪周一表示，将与其中国合资伙伴上汽集团共同开发针对中国的新智能电动汽车平台。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/audi-partner-saic-develop-china-specific-ev-platform-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>彭博社报道，中国监管机构计划召开欧洲投资者会议以重振股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulators-plan-european-investor-meet-revive-stocks-bloomberg-reports-2024-05-20/</link><description>彭博社周一援引不愿透露姓名的知情人士的话报道称，中国市场监管机构计划本周与欧洲投资者举行会议，以重振他们对全球第二大股市的兴趣。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-regulators-plan-european-investor-meet-revive-stocks-bloomberg-reports-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>新台湾总统就任后台中关系的关键事实</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/key-facts-taiwan-china-relations-new-taiwan-president-takes-office-2024-05-20/</link><description>台湾总统赖清德在一月份赢得选举后于周一就职。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 06:34:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/key-facts-taiwan-china-relations-new-taiwan-president-takes-office-2024-05-20/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾敦促中国允许对有争议的南海浅滩进行审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-should-allow-scrutiny-disputed-shoal-2024-05-20/</link><description>在指责北京破坏黄岩岛海洋环境后，菲律宾周一挑战中国开放黄岩岛接受国际监督。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 03:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-should-allow-scrutiny-disputed-shoal-2024-05-20/</guid></item></channel></rss>